{"tid":1881054,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"簡單阿里巴巴(9988)分析 - 細看阿里2020年事件","createTime":"2020-02-15T09:38:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-15T16:21:14.000Z","uid":316667,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"bb0c9e025b829d01c58f58a7e50d56bced41a8e5","tid":1881054,"uid":316667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T09:38:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8z8NiKf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8z8NiKf.png&h=c1ad95a9&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n今日開一開9988既走勢圖，發現呢隻股既波幅開始收細。小弟才疏學淺，以前簡單睇過坊間既股票書，講波幅開始收細，意味股票會開始爆單邊，而到底阿里會爆上定爆落呢？小弟大膽估計會爆上，並會以阿里今年至今發生既事件分析點解會有以上睇法！<br />\n(1) 美國伊朗2020年1月4日開戰，9988股價由1月3日收報的212元，跌到1月8日收報的210.8元。<br />\n<br />\n(2)武漢肺炎危機，由阿里1月14日最高位的223.6元，跌至1月31日的200.4元。<br />\n<br />\n(3)軟銀解禁憂慮，由2月6日收報的217.4元跌到2月11日收報的212.2元。軟銀創辦人兼行政總裁孫正義大派定心丸，睇好阿里既發展<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2563756/%E8%BB%9F%E9%8A%80%E5%AD%AB%E6%AD%A3%E7%BE%A9%EF%BC%9A%E4%B8%8D%E6%80%A5%E6%96%BC%E5%87%BA%E5%94%AE%E9%98%BF%E9%87%8C%E5%B7%B4%E5%B7%B4%E8%82%A1%E6%AC%8A%E3%80%80%E4%BF%A1%E4%BB%8D%E6%9C%89%E5%A4%A7%E9%87%8F%E5%A2%9E%E9%95%B7%E7%A9%BA%E9%96%93\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2563756%2F%25E8%25BB%259F%25E9%258A%2580%25E5%25AD%25AB%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E7%25BE%25A9%25EF%25BC%259A%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%2580%25A5%25E6%2596%25BC%25E5%2587%25BA%25E5%2594%25AE%25E9%2598%25BF%25E9%2587%258C%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E8%2582%25A1%25E6%25AC%258A%25E3%2580%2580%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E4%25BB%258D%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%2587%258F%25E5%25A2%259E%25E9%2595%25B7%25E7%25A9%25BA%25E9%2596%2593&d=uD1rvIJwXfBqs1i1iclFxyUaeeTarj8%2BpjPG%2B7PQGFg%3D&h=25d03ad2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2563756/%E8%BB%9F%E9%8A%80%E5%AD%AB%E6%AD%A3%E7%BE%A9%EF%BC%9A%E4%B8%8D%E6%80%A5%E6%96%BC%E5%87%BA%E5%94%AE%E9%98%BF%E9%87%8C%E5%B7%B4%E5%B7%B4%E8%82%A1%E6%AC%8A%E3%80%80%E4%BF%A1%E4%BB%8D%E6%9C%89%E5%A4%A7%E9%87%8F%E5%A2%9E%E9%95%B7%E7%A9%BA%E9%96%93</a><br />\n<br />\n(4)美東時間2月13日，阿里發布大超預期的業績後，集團執行長張勇在回答問題的環節，表達出對武漢肺炎對於集團第4季業績的憂慮，翌日港股下跌2.2元，2月14日收報215元。<br />\n<br />\n由此可見，阿里於多次事件後，慢慢建立自己的支持位，多次的大事件也看得出好多朋友用金錢大大力支持阿里。而隨著武漢肺炎的憂慮慢慢消退，唯一阻礙阿里上升的絆腳石消除，看好阿里繼續穩步上揚。<br />\n<br />\n以上只為本人小小分析，還望各位大佬指正"},{"pid":"b55823c6e53488b944784e349529806ba58e413a","tid":1881054,"uid":177120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T10:16:56.000Z","msg":"9988有機會上 買美股定港股好"},{"pid":"965493e6b6a61f228fa2844551d79b2bb0da5262","tid":1881054,"uid":237825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T10:32:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"703729a2d3c3196c0ef4b9fd0f78f67f82fda203","tid":1881054,"uid":67257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T10:44:32.000Z","msg":"下星期估計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abdfb627b3e24c1103abc963614c593b56801eeb","tid":1881054,"uid":141630,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T11:12:28.000Z","msg":"ipo仲未走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"561f58671d6c568502f70c9514f674c6a3cda940","tid":1881054,"uid":68594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"703729a2d3c3196c0ef4b9fd0f78f67f82fda203","tid":1881054,"uid":67257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T10:44:32.000Z","msg":"下星期估計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T12:53:56.000Z","msg":"星期五會225"},{"pid":"bfa5e853321601fdf27edb238a64ed153dd53d01","tid":1881054,"uid":128781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T16:21:14.000Z","msg":"應該跌"}]}